
pex_harness examples/lookup
----------------------------------------------

This example demonstrates that the locations of directory spaces are available
to application Stages through a lookup dictionary that is part of the generic
Stage class: 

By default this example will run with the Pipeline with one Slice on a single node.
Edit the MPI machinefile "nodelist.scr" to specify the hostname of the current host.

The pipeline is then executed via

% ./run.sh lookup_policy.paf   <some-run-id>

such as

% ./run.sh lookup_policy.paf  gds_10066

Executing the example will give entries in the log files like:

Pipeline.log :

lsst.pexhexamples.pipeline.MyLookupStage.preprocess:  dirWork /lsst/daues/lsst4/add_ons/222/examples/lookup/gds_10066/.
lsst.pexhexamples.pipeline.MyLookupStage.preprocess:  dirInput /lsst/daues/lsst4/add_ons/222/examples/lookup/gds_10066/.
lsst.pexhexamples.pipeline.MyLookupStage.preprocess:  dirOutput /lsst/daues/lsst4/add_ons/222/examples/lookup/gds_10066/.
lsst.pexhexamples.pipeline.MyLookupStage.preprocess:  dirUpdate /lsst/daues/lsst4/add_ons/222/examples/lookup/gds_10066/.
lsst.pexhexamples.pipeline.MyLookupStage.preprocess:  dirScratch /lsst/daues/lsst4/add_ons/222/examples/lookup/gds_10066/.

Slice0.log 

lsst.pexhexamples.pipeline.MyLookupStage.process:  dirWork /lsst/daues/lsst4/add_ons/222/examples/lookup/gds_10066/.
lsst.pexhexamples.pipeline.MyLookupStage.process:  dirInput /lsst/daues/lsst4/add_ons/222/examples/lookup/gds_10066/.
lsst.pexhexamples.pipeline.MyLookupStage.process:  dirOutput /lsst/daues/lsst4/add_ons/222/examples/lookup/gds_10066/.
lsst.pexhexamples.pipeline.MyLookupStage.process:  dirUpdate /lsst/daues/lsst4/add_ons/222/examples/lookup/gds_10066/.
lsst.pexhexamples.pipeline.MyLookupStage.process:  dirScratch /lsst/daues/lsst4/add_ons/222/examples/lookup/gds_10066/.



